OL,3,C'I wanted to give up': Sexual assault
OL,4,Csurvivor speaks about the court process
OL,6,FA sexual assault survivor has waived
OL,7,Fher anonymity to share her story and
OL,8,F'empower others' to bring their
OL,9,Fattacker to court.
OL,11,FNatalie Brown was repeatedly groped by
OL,12,F58-year-old Graeme Dea in an
OL,13,FInnerleithen bar in 2024. Despite
OL,14,Ffeeling shaken after the incident, she
OL,15,Freported it to police the next day.
OL,17,FDea denied the offence but was found
OL,18,Fguilty of sexual assault, and was
OL,19,Ffined and given a harassment order at
OL,20,FSelkirk Sheriff Court on Monday
OL,21,FJanuary 19, 2026.
