OL,3,C'I wanted to give up': Sexual assault
OL,4,Csurvivor speaks about the court process
OL,6,FNatalie said: "It's horrible, you
OL,7,Fliterally just freeze. You don't know
OL,8,Fwhat to say or do for the best.
OL,10,F"A lot of people did say to me: 'Why
OL,11,Fdidn't you just tell him to stop it',
OL,12,For 'just slap him around the face'.
OL,13,FIt's not as easy as that at all."
OL,15,FNatalie says she did not comprehend
OL,16,Fthe extent of the assault until she
OL,17,Freturned home.
