OL,3,C'I wanted to give up': Sexual assault
OL,4,Csurvivor speaks about the court process
OL,6,FShe said: "That night it didn't really
OL,7,Fsink in, I didn't think anything of it
OL,8,Funtil I came home and spoke to my
OL,9,Fhusband about it."
OL,11,FThe bar had CCTV footage of the
OL,12,Fassault which was played in court.
OL,14,FReflecting on the court process,
OL,15,FNatalie said: "It was really hard, the
OL,16,Fwhole process is really hard and
OL,17,Freally long. Knowing I had the CCTV
OL,18,Fevidence to back up what I was saying
OL,19,Freally did help.
