OL,3,C'I wanted to give up': Sexual assault
OL,4,Csurvivor speaks about the court process
OL,6,F"If it's your word against theirs then
OL,7,Fit is a lot harder to get a
OL,8,Fconviction."
OL,10,FDespite this, Natalie urges other
OL,11,Fvictims of sexual assault to tell the
OL,12,Fpolice.
OL,14,FNatalie said: "I wanted to make people
OL,15,Faware that yeah, it is a really hard
OL,16,Fprocess, and it can be a long, drawn-
OL,17,Fout thing.
OL,19,F"There can be delays, or things happen
OL,20,Fthat get in the way. But you've just
OL,21,Fgot to keep on fighting.
