OL,3,C'I wanted to give up': Sexual assault
OL,4,Csurvivor speaks about the court process
OL,6,F"I wanted to give up during the court
OL,7,Fcase. I broke down in court, I thought
OL,8,F'I can't do this'.
OL,10,F"But it's definitely worth it because
OL,11,Fwhen you do get the conviction, it
OL,12,Fmakes you feel better. That you have
OL,13,Fstood up to them, and they can't do it
OL,14,Fto anybody else."
OL,16,FSandy Brindley from Rape Crisis
OL,17,FScotland reflected on Natalie's
OL,18,Fexperience.
