OL,3,C'I wanted to give up': Sexual assault
OL,4,Csurvivor speaks about the court process
OL,6,F"Sexual assault continues to be an
OL,7,Funder-reported crime. The reasons
OL,8,Fpeople give to us for not reporting
OL,9,Fare things like fear of not being
OL,10,Fbelieved, fear of the process itself,
OL,11,F(whether) it will be the (victim's)
OL,12,Fword against (the accused)."
OL,14,FMs Brindley says Rape Crisis Scotland
OL,15,Foffers help to victims of sexual
OL,16,Fassault, and those going through the
OL,17,Fcourts.
