OL,3,C'I wanted to give up': Sexual assault
OL,4,Csurvivor speaks about the court process
OL,6,FShe said: "I think it's really
OL,7,Fimportant to know you do not need to
OL,8,Fgo through the process alone. We have
OL,9,Fadvocacy workers across Scotland who
OL,10,Fare there to support you from the
OL,11,Fstart of the process to the finish."
OL,13,FIf you have been affected by Natalie's
OL,14,Fstory, you can find details of help
OL,15,Fand support here.
